Package: Friedman
Title: Tools for Exploring and Modeling Data in R
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Orestes", "Gonzalez", email = "orestesgonzalez@usf.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides functions for exploring, cleaning, visualizing, and
    modeling datasets in R. The package is designed for students and beginner
    analysts who want a simple workflow for data preparation, summary
    statistics, visualization, and basic predictive analysis.
Depends: 
    R (>= 3.1.2)
Imports: 
    ggplot2,
    dplyr
License: CC0
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 7.3.3
URL: https://github.com/INFO/Friedman
BugReports: https://github.com/INFO/Friedman/issues
